OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday, Friday and Saturday are
OL,7,Flikely to remain mostly dry and
OL,8,Fbreezy, with some clear or sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Temperatures close or a little
OL,10,Fabove average throughout.
